          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2161.-step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once very hot, add the<strong> spice-crusted steak[s] </strong>to the pan</p><p>For rare, cook for 2 min max on each side; for medium-rare, cook for 2-3 min on each side; for medium, cook for 3-4 min on each side</p><p>Once the steak is cooked, transfer to a plate to rest</p>",
      "order": 3,
