      "instruction": "<p>Drain and rinse your<strong> black beans</strong></p><p>Once the steak is done, wipe out the steak pan with kitchen paper and return it to a medium heat</p><p>Add the<strong> drained black beans</strong> and <strong>soy sauce</strong> and cook for 1-2 min or until warmed through</p>",
